隐私政策
本软件《行山记》深知个人隐私的重要性，并致力于保护您的数据安全。本隐私政策将说明我们如何处理您的信息。
1. 数据收集与使用
本软件为完全离线工具，不会收集、上传或共享任何您的个人数据。所有徒步计划、装备库和个人记录均仅存储在您的本地设备中。
2. 数据存储
您的所有数据（包括徒步计划、装备信息、导入的个人记录等）均保存在设备本地存储空间内，不会与第三方共享。
3. 数据导入与导出
本软件支持用户通过 XLSX 文件等方式进行个人数据导入与导出。所有导入导出操作均需用户主动触发，本软件不会进行任何自动传输。
4. 数据安全
由于所有数据仅存储于本地，数据安全取决于您对设备的管理。本软件不承担因设备遗失、损坏或被第三方获取而造成的数据泄露责任。
5. 隐私政策更新
本隐私政策可能会因功能更新而调整。更新后的内容将在应用内展示，并自发布之日起生效。
最后更新日期：2025年8月29日


Privacy Policy
This application, "Hikememo", understands the importance of personal privacy and is committed to protecting your data security. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information.
1. Data Collection and Usage
This application is a completely offline tool. It does not collect, upload, or share any of your personal data. All hiking plans, equipment inventories, and personal records are stored exclusively on your local device.
2. Data Storage
All your data (including hiking plans, equipment information, imported personal records, etc.) is saved in the local storage of your device and will not be shared with any third parties.
3. Data Import and Export
The application supports user-initiated data import and export via methods such as XLSX files. All import and export operations must be actively triggered by the user; the application will not perform any automatic data transfers.
4. Data Security
As all data is stored locally, data security depends on your management of the device. This application is not responsible for data breaches resulting from the loss, damage, or third-party acquisition of your device.
5. Privacy Policy Updates
This privacy policy may be adjusted due to feature updates. The updated content will be displayed within the application and will take effect from the date of its publication.
Last Updated: August 29, 2025
